commit 44b1a56fffaa483b6974394ddb2c9a8ec7dfeaf3
Author: Daniel Falbel <dfalbel@gmail.com>
Date:   Thu Apr 16 15:37:01 2026 -0300

    Remove dead generic dispatch code paths

    Delete call_c_function, do_call, .dispatch_cache, clean_names,
    make_cpp_function_name, cpp_clean_names, cpp_make_function_name,
    create_fn_name, and cpp_suffix. All generated code now uses direct calls,
    inline R dispatch, or C++ dispatchers.

    Replace torch:::cpp_make_function_name in torchgen with a pure-R
    implementation so codegen no longer depends on the removed C++ function.
