    CRAN release v0.17.0 (#1433)

    * Prepare CRAN release v0.17.0

    - Bump version to 0.17.0
    - Set branch to cran/v0.17.0 for lantern binary downloads
    - Uncomment CRAN submission lines in .Rbuildignore
    - Polish NEWS.md entries

    * Add .superset to .Rbuildignore

    Fixes CRAN check warning about hidden directory.

    * Fix CRAN check issues: .superset in Rbuildignore, URLs in vignette

    - Add .superset to .Rbuildignore
    - Update moved NVIDIA CUDA GPUs URL (301 redirect)
    - Use fully qualified URL for compatibility-matrix link

    * Remove Remotes field from DESCRIPTION

    RcppCore/Rcpp remote is not needed for CRAN release.

    * Fix signed/unsigned integer comparison warnings

    Use size_t or R_xlen_t for loop variables compared against
    container .size() or .length() to eliminate -Wsign-compare warnings
    flagged by win-builder.

    * maintainer
